---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../config';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<h1>üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to your <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> blog starter template, modified
				to support <a href="https://tina.io/">Tina CMS</a>. This template serves as a lightweight,
				minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build a personal website or blog with Astro.
			</p>
			<p>
				This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
				<code>astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
				<a href="https://astro.build/integrations">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
				React, or Vue to your project.
			</p>
			<p>Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Spin up your CMS with <code>npm run tina</code> then head to <a href="/admin/index.html">/admin/index.html</a></li>
				<li>Edit this page in <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li>Edit the site header items in <code>src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li>Add your name to the footer in <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code>src/content/</code></li>
				<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>read the Astro docs
				</a> or <a href="https://astro.build/chat">join them on Discord</a> to ask questions.
				For help with the CMS, check out <a href="https://tina.io/docs/">the Tina documentation</a>
				or join their <a href="https://discord.com/invite/zumN63Ybpf">Discord server</a>.
			</p>
			<p>Have fun! I'm <a href="https://www.bennet.org/">Tom Bennet</a> - if you would like to suggest
				improvements to this template, please consider <a href="https://github.com/tombennet/astro-tina-starter">
			  submitting a PR</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
